## Project Summary

This project explored multiple torque-control strategies for DC motors from a modeling and comparative-analysis perspective.

## Scope

- Motor-equation derivation and analytical formulation.
- Control-method comparison.
- MATLAB-based torque-speed visualization.
- Performance interpretation for each method.

## Outcome

The report presents a clear electrical-machine control study grounded in equations, plots, and method comparison.
